title: Distribution Board
description: Maintenance activities for Distribution Board in LV SWGR system

body.raw:
# Distribution Board


## Insulation

- Ins. Resist.
- Phase-Phase Test
- Phase-Earth Test


## Busbar

- Busbar Tightness
- Connection Test
- Thermal Scan


## Voltage

- Volt. Stability
- Voltage Drop


## Verification

- Phase Seq. Verif.
- Labeling Check


## Protection

- Func. Breaker-RCD Coord.
- RCD Test Button
- Earth Connection
